OL,3,CMan who doused his former partner's
OL,4,Cteenage son in petrol jailed
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for six years
OL,7,Ffor an arson attack in Hampshire.
OL,9,F55-year-old Darren Waring doused his
OL,10,Fformer partner's teenage son in
OL,11,Fpetrol, at an address in Park Gate,
OL,12,Fbefore setting the lounge on fire in
OL,13,FDecember last year.
OL,15,FAngered by the recent breakdown of the
OL,16,Frelationship, he attended his ex-
OL,17,Fpartner's address where he poured
OL,18,Fpetrol over her car and made a trail
OL,19,Ftowards the house.
