OL,6,FHe also poured petrol over his ex-
OL,7,Fpartner's teenager whilst assaulting
OL,8,Fhim and making threats, during which
OL,9,Fhe attempted to spark a lighter.
OL,11,FBoth victims managed to escape to a
OL,12,Fneighbour's house.
OL,14,FDC Heather Milsom, who investigated
OL,15,Fthis case, says: "This was a shocking
OL,16,Fdisplay of domestic violence which
OL,17,Fleft Waring's ex-partner and her
OL,18,Ffamily extremely distressed, and put
OL,19,Ftheir lives at risk of serious harm.
